  • Constructor Details

    • Service

      public Service​(java.lang.String name, java.util.Date startDate, java.util.Date endDate, Day[] occurrences, int capacityMax, java.lang.String comment, int fee, java.util.Date serviceTime, java.lang.String profNo) throws java.text.ParseException, InvalidFormatException
      Creates a service using the provided fields after verifying their format. Also generates a new service code for the service.
      Parameters:
      name - Service name
      startDate - Service start date
      endDate - Service end date
      occurrences - Service weekly recurrence
      capacityMax - Service maximum capacity
      comment - Service comment
      fee - Service fee
      serviceTime - Service time
      profNo - Service professional's number
      Throws:
      java.text.ParseException - in case of unexpected behaviour while parsing a date
      InvalidFormatException - if any of the fields does not respect the imposed format
